First described from the Central North Pacific (
Tendal & Hessler, 1977
), subsequently from ∼ 
5770 m
water depth on the Nares Abyssal Plain, north-west Atlantic (

Schröder 
et al
., 1989

) and at two stations (2790 and 
4912 m
) in the Cape Basin (
